{"word":"καρποφόρος","slug":"καρποφόρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καρποφόρος</b></el> <el>(καρπο-φόρος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φέρω'><el>φέρω</el></a>\n<p/><i>fruit-bearing, fruitful</i>, of trees, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; of lands, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; of Demeter, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}